Quick tip: Apply hot oil and massage! Hot oil treatments are great for any hair type and are like a spa for your tresses. It help to strengthen and prevent dry, brittle hair and also split ends. It is also useful to stimulate blood flow, as well as helping with hair growth, preventing dandruff, dry scalp, frizziness, moisture and much more.
